16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
18 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
19 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Safeguarding
20 American Veteran Empowerment Act (or SAVE Act)".
21 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
22 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 239 of Title 44, unless there is
23 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
24 A. For purposes of this section:
